{"tid":406402,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"郭文貴爆料，香港某建制派常往東莞嫖娼，專揀處女","createTime":"2017-09-19T15:30:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-05T01:17:51.000Z","uid":89349,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2eca457b494e08f8aac23bac0fbc4d0bcf2eeacc","tid":406402,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:30:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n他又透露，中共控制香港富商、官員及議員有四大方法：<br />\n<br />\n（一）搜集貪污行賄證據；<br />\n<br />\n（二）引誘他們到大陸嫖娼後拍攝淫亂視頻；<br />\n<br />\n（三）中共官二富二代與港商政要做生意，建立利益關係，或偷錄其船上賭博記錄；<br />\n<br />\n（四）大規模派人滲入並控制香港各大行業。"},{"pid":"52a19f6484589b7711893c3b6642ac49e6a613ad","tid":406402,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:31:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">淚</span></span>"},{"pid":"c9fb4e44047fe31c31976110aa00e24e883e9229","tid":406402,"uid":6297,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:32:39.000Z","msg":"(二）係唔係湯渣"},{"pid":"056788a806dc67ff0af93dab4b93422332aa1265","tid":406402,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:32:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">淚</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e349b064612d7901b58b5388a8bbb9e53f020c49","tid":406402,"uid":30214,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:33:05.000Z","msg":"條友又9 up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"479c4eb64c0e1dc5657c311867684d3bd1baedd6","tid":406402,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:33:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>(二）係唔係湯渣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n爸打眼利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"993c443263bef8e6521c5d03c5d151f179fdec2f","tid":406402,"uid":92